If you want to burn this, you proboarly noticed that it is not an image file. You need some DVD-Recoding program, or atleast a program that can burn raw dvd movie. Use Nero Recode or Nero Startsmart -> Burningroom/express is what i would recommend. I dont think that Alcohol 120% could burn this, because it is a program based on image files.
